com.interpss.core.acsc

Interface AcscBranch

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AclfBranch, Branch, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ExtensionElement, IAclfBranch, IAclfBranchAdaptation, IAclfBranchAdjustment, IAclfBranchFunc, IAcscBranch, IAdaptable, IBranchSwitchBreakModel, NameTag, NetworkedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DStabBranch, Dynamic3PBranch, Steady3PBranch
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AcscBranchImpl, DStabBranchImpl, Dynamic3PBranchImpl, Steady3PBranchImpl

    public interface AcscBranch
extends AclfBranch, IAcscBranch
    A representation of the model object 'Branch'. * ACSCBranch * * (1) Positive sequence, use aclf branch data to calculate * * (2) Negative sequence, use aclf branch data to calculate. It may be fifferent than the positive * sequence if the branch is a PSXfr. * * (3) Zero sequence, for Line type, use z0 and hB0 to calculate. For Xfr or PSXfr type, use z0 and * from side ground type, from side ground Z and to side ground type, to side ground z to calculate. AcscBranch could be extended using IAascBranch interface

    The following features are supported:

    • Z0
    • HB0
    • Xfr From Connect Code
    • Xfr To Connect Code
    • Xfr From Ground Z
    • Xfr To Ground Z
    See Also:
    AcscPackage.getAcscBranch()
